# Project uses yarn (see "packageManager" in package.json). Committed
# npm lockfiles drift out of sync with what yarn installs and cause
# noisy "extraneous" warnings when electron-builder shells out to
# `npm ls` during packaging. Keep yarn.lock as the single source of
# truth for the dependency graph.
package-lock.json

